Prophetus smiled. The predacons finally came to life. He knew they 
were well in range of the defenses so he decided to play... daringly.

Prophetus: I am Prophetus, and I represent the Tripredacus. I am 
accompanied by Jetstorm and Anachronox. We are here to establish a 
garden, and if you wish, maybe discuss with the neighbors. Our 
commander, Daemos, will arrive shortly.

Jetstorm stands still, gripping thightly his tomahawks.

--------------------------
Meanwhile, Daemos was about 100 km away from there.
